Count how many students met MAP growth expectations, using custom groups

Usage

tabulate_map_growth(.x, ...)

Arguments

.x

<data.frame> the MAP growth data to tabulate

...

<dynamic-dots> names of columns to group by

Value

a data frame with the ... fields, "Met", "Students", and "Percent"
